fields.name: Waxy Finish Chelsea Boots
fields.description:
A staple in every gentleman's wardrobe since the 60s', the Chelsea boot has been recognised as one of the most comfortable, multi-use boots featuring rich waxy leather, Ortholite Foam insole for all-day comfort and breathability, under elastic gussets and heel loop tab for an easier/quicker get on and off.


Next - Your ultimate style destination for all of life’s essentials. With quality at the heart of everything we do, Next interprets the latest trends to create modern, effortless, easy-to-style pieces for your home and wardrobe. The hottest brands and the latest trends: find them all here.

Upper - Leather, Lining & Sock - Other Materials, Textile, Sole - Other Materials.

fields.name: Desert Boots
fields.description:
A plain front, round-toe tan brown leather desert boot that is tough and practical. With a supple leather upper, lace-up fastening, and hardy rubber soles. Made with Ortholite® insoles for all-day comfort and breathability.
Upper - Leather, Lining & Sock - Textile, Leather, Sole - Other Materials.

fields.name: Dune London Crannes Apron Wedge Hiker Boots
fields.description:
Upgrade your wardrobe with our new men's casual boot. A casual take on a classic hiking style they feature a lightweight chunky treaded sole and exposed stitching detail. Secured with an internal zip they are lined for extra comfort.
Upper - 100% Other fibres. Lining - 100% Other fibres. Sole - 100% Other fibres.

fields.name: Lift, Slim And Shape Skinny Jeans
fields.description:
Show Less
Looking for jeans that really do figure hug and flatter? You're in the right place. Our Lift, Slim and Shape jeans in inky blue will instantly transform your look.

Made from a cotton-rich blend with extra stretch, these skinny jeans have been designed with cleverly hidden support which sculps your figure and a high waistband to contour your shape. The waist smoothing and shaping doesn't end there, they are designed with a clever pattern and curved gap free waistband to support and slim. In a high rise, fitted through the hip and thigh with a slim leg. Made with LYCRA EcoMade elastane to provide lasting comfort, fit and shape, these jeans have performance benefits that won’t wash out. Crying out for a tucked in top, you've got this trend nailed.

fields.name: Cropped Slim Jeans
fields.description:
Show Less
Mid rise
Cropped tapered leg
Tummy sculpting
Fitted through the hips and thighs
Your favourite jeans with a seasonal refresh. Made in a soft stretch cotton denim for all day comfort, these cropped jeans are designed in a mid rise that’s comfortable for all body types and offers more support around the midsection. Compatible with any length top, these jeans are a great go-to staple for your wardrobe. Figure hugging through the hips and thigh, they taper to a slim leg that finishes at the calf.
Regular inside leg length 25" / 63cm.
Tall inside leg length 30.5" / 78cm.
Machine washable.
94% Cotton, 5% Polyester, 1% Lycra® Elastane.
